               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝggʷā, Antiphonary for the entire year (fols. 2ra-57rc)
 II)
                     Mǝʿrāf, The Common of the Office (57rc-105rc)
 II-1) Kǝśtat za-ʾaryām, The
                     festive Office (fols. 57rc-63rc)
 II-2) Wāzemā, The Office of Vigils (fols.
                     63rc-70va)
 II-3) Sǝbḥāta nagh, The Office of Matins (fols. 70va-75rc)
                     II-4) Mawaddǝs, The Sunday Office (fols. 75rc-102va, 103ra-105rc)
 
                     Additiones 1-3.</summary>
